ml_tags: Yindi Ruby Clarke Forever 21 22-04-2000 - 30-05-2021 Forever in our hearts Butchulla woman First Indigenous woman in infantry She loved her culture and her God Much loved sister to Tinka and Maidie Loved daughter of Leilani, and sister of Ikey, Pearl, Norman and Leilani (jnr) Yindi joined the Australian Army in August 2019 Yindi loved boxing and boxed for Brophy's Proud "Bagalim wulgu" fighting girl Owens Clan
